        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "Edward, according to the portraits, always wore a flat cap, the base of the crown ornamented with bands of jewels.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5233_39051_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "The Bluecoat Boys, and long may they have the sense to keep to their dress, show us exactly the ordinary dress of the citizen, except that the modern knickerbocker has taken the place of the trunks.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5233_39051_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "That peculiar fashion of the previous reign-the enormously broad shouldered appearance-still held in this reign to some extent, though the collars of the jerkins, or, as one may more easily know them, overcoats or jackets, open garments, were not so wide, and allowed more of the puffed shoulder of the sleeve to show.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5233_39051_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "Indeed, the collar became quite small, as in the Windsor Holbein painting of Edward, and the puff in the shoulders not so rotund.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5233_39051_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "The doublet of this reign shows no change, but the collar of the shirt begins to show signs of the ruff of later years.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5233_39051_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "It is no larger, but is generally left untied with the ornamental strings hanging.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5233_39051_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "Hall, the author of 'Satires,' fifteen ninety eight, speaks of a man, an effeminate dandy, as wearing a partlet strip.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5233_39051_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "Henry the eighth. wore a band about his neck, the forerunner of the ruff. Some of his bands were of silver cloth with ruffs to them, others, as I have shown, were wonderfully embroidered.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5233_39051_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "Dress, on the whole, is much plainer, sleeves are not so full of cuts and slashes, and they fit more closely to the arm.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5233_39051_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "Shoes are not cut about at the toe quite with the same splendour, but are still broad in the toe.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5233_39051_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "For the women, it may be said that the change towards simplicity is even more marked.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5233_39051_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "The very elaborate head dress, the folded, diamond shaped French hood has disappeared almost entirely, and, for the rich, the half hoop, set back from the forehead with a piece of velvet or silk to hang down the back, will best describe the head gear.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5233_39051_000021_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000021_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "From that to the centre pointed hoop shows the trend of the shape.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5233_39051_000021_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000021_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "This latest form of woman's head apparel was born, I think, out of the folds of the linen cap worn in the house, and this, being repeated in the velvet night caps, became the extreme of fashion.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5233_39051_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "It is a high collar and very open in front, showing a piece of the under dress.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5233_39051_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5233/39051/5233_39051_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5233",
        "content": "The same stiff bodied appearance holds good, but in more simple dresses the skirts were not quite as voluminous as heretofore.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
]